OL,3,CSkipper's near miss after boat
OL,4,Ccapsizes near Exmouth
OL,6,FInvestigations looking into a fishing
OL,7,Fvessel that went down off the coast of
OL,8,FExmouth have been completed.
OL,10,FOn 18 June 2021, a fishing vessel
OL,11,Fcalled Angelena capsized and sank
OL,12,Faround eight miles south-east of
OL,13,FExmouth.
OL,15,FThe skipper, who was working on the
OL,16,Fvessel alone, had been attempting to
OL,17,Fland a catch on deck at the time.
