OL,3,CSkipper's near miss after boat
OL,4,Ccapsizes near Exmouth
OL,6,FThe skipper activated the personal
OL,7,Flocator beacon once in the liferaft
OL,8,Fand was rescued unharmed by a nearby
OL,9,Fvessel around 40 minutes later.
OL,11,FThe Marine Accident Investigation
OL,12,FBranch report said: "Angelena was not
OL,13,Frequired to undergo a stability
OL,14,Fassessment nor had recommended roll or
OL,15,Fheel tests been conducted to identify
OL,16,Fpotential stability issues.
