OL,3,CSkipper's near miss after boat
OL,4,Ccapsizes near Exmouth
OL,6,F"Further, no guidance was available
OL,7,Ffor operating a vessel of Angelena's
OL,8,Fsize alone and a crew of more than one
OL,9,Fperson was known to have formed the
OL,10,Fbasis of its risk assessments.
OL,12,F"The low fuel levels and excessive
OL,13,Fload in the suspended net lowered the
OL,14,Fmargins of stability, which caused the
OL,15,Frapid capsize and loss of Angelena."
OL,17,FThe skipper was "experienced and
OL,18,Fqualified" but unaware of stability
OL,19,Frisks, according to the report.
