OL,4,Ccapsizes near Exmouth
OL,6,FIt said: "The skipper was fortunate to
OL,7,Fenter the water uninjured and be able
OL,8,Fto inflate and board Angelena's
OL,9,Fliferaft and raise the alarm."
OL,11,FAs a result of these findings,
OL,12,Frecommendations have been made to the
OL,13,FMaritime and Coastguard Agency to
OL,14,Fimprove fishers' understanding of
OL,15,Fstability, require risk assessments
OL,16,Fthat define minimum crewing levels for
OL,17,Ffishing operations.
